defaultWe studied the tissue distribution 
defaultin the body 
defaultof the abnormal prion protein in vCJD, and found that in addition to accumulating in the central nervous sy
defaults
defaulttem (CNS), it was widely distributed in lymphoid tissues throughout the body, including the spleen, lymph nodes, tonsil
defaults
